reviewText: Great tips for anyone truly interested in playing volleyball seriously to win.
Excellent, point by point instruction, demonstration and drills for each of the basic skills.
very happy with quality content of dvd
This is a great video.  we have used her you tube videos to teach some of the basics of volleyball to my teams in the past.  worth the time and the money!

This DVD is great for someone just learning the game or trying to perfect their form.  I started playing beach volleyball last year at the age of 37.  It's a lot harder than what I remembered in high school gym class!  This DVD definitely has given me tools on how to perfect my form so I can play harder.  I highly recommend this DVD.
